{
  "stem": "14060.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Ludwig Weiler, spelled W-E-I-L-E-R, the surname.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ludwig is my first name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Originally, where I was born being in Hungary, coming from the place called Sopron-- in German, Odenburg-- on the Austro-Hungarian border.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was called in Hungarian 'Lajas,' which is the equivalent of Ludwig.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my nickname, if you like to call it that, was Laci.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lajas is spelled L-A-J-A-S.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Laci is L-A-C-I.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born on the 14th of March, 1930, being the Hebrew date of Purim.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And consequently, I'm just over 66 by a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was Sopron, Odenburg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was Hungary, on the border town of Austria.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even though I was 14 years of age when we were deported in July 1944, I do have quite vivid recollection from approximately 1936.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I do remember, very clearly, listening to a radio, which we had at the time of the Duke of Windsor, as he was known later, Edward the XIII's abdication.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that is basically a very clear event, historical event, which I do remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Subsequently to that, maybe due to the unusual circumstances of the '30s, and obviously in the '40s, one was what one might call today pre-aged.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one got into conversation with adults on daily events, which-- maybe not everybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in my case, I think it has had an influence of being aware of what we knew, which of course wasn't everything which was happening.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could basically start from the time I started school in Sopron.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was an Orthodox and Neolog community, as it was from the time in the 1870s.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They split the communities, except for about two, three towns where they had what they called Status Quo communities, which meant they did not split.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
